🕹️ HOW TO PLAY
Player 1 starts.

Click "Roll Dice" 🎲 — the number you roll (except 1) is added to your Current Score.

If you roll a 1, your becomes 0, and the turn switches to the next player.

To avoid risk, click "Hold" — your Turn Score gets added to your Current Score.

The first player to reach 100 Current Score and click "Hold" wins the game! 🏆
🔄 New game
🎲 Roll dice
📥 Hold
